{"tid":1675754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"所羅門群島裁定中國租賃島嶼合約違法　必須終止","createTime":"2019-10-26T05:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T06:46:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30cd9149546639848425a4a869b478aa5923ff9e","tid":1675754,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.drishtiias.com/images/uploads/1571301703_image3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drishtiias.com%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2F1571301703_image3.jpg&h=0b4ed3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月與中國建交的太平洋島國所羅門群島表示，國內中央省早前與中國森田企業簽署租賃圖拉吉島的合約違法，所羅門群島總理索加瓦雷發聲明表示，有關合約必須立即終止。<br />\n<br />\n協議於上月22日，即中所建交第二日簽署，協議長達75年，訂明森田企業擁有圖拉吉島及周邊島嶼的獨家開發權，司法部長表示，這項協議未有送交司法部長辦公室審查，是非法、不可強制執行、必須立即終結生效。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部長埃斯帕讚揚所羅門群島的做法，認為是強化主權、透明度與法治的重要決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488334-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488334-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=0ab367cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488334-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1875dcb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488334-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5a5a40c82b9e65e1b2daa240322a278f58fb0a23","tid":1675754,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1029 沙田新城市中庭見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">城大和你傾<br />\n無懼校方打壓<br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港新一大！真CU打壓學術自由：「城大和你傾」轉場通知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/